# Implements the "structured PR + code review" half of the GitHub-workflow
# proposal. Any change to the paths below REQUIRES security review before merge.
# Pair this with branch protection on `main` (require PR review + certification
# workflow as a required status check) — CODEOWNERS routes review but does not
# itself enforce it.
